Benjamin C. STEWART
v.
William DAVIS. No. 352P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 12, 2004.

William Davis, Pro Se.

C. Colon Willoughby, Jr., District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 8th day of July 2004 by Plaintiff to order relinquishment of documents:
